Interface FileLocationModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.syncleus.ferma.ElementFrame, FileReferenceModel, ToFileModelTransformable, com.syncleus.ferma.VertexFrame, WindupFrame<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex>, WindupVertexFrame
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    HardcodedIPLocationModel, InlineHintModel, JavaAnnotationTypeReferenceModel, JavaTypeReferenceModel, XmlTypeReferenceModel

    public interface FileLocationModel
extends FileReferenceModel, ToFileModelTransformable
    Refers to a specific portion of a File and contains a reference to the code involved.
